6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Craiyon and StarryAI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Upscaling. Where Craiyon pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Batch Generation and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, StarryAI uniquely offers Style Transfer and Commercial License, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Craiyon holds an overall score of 4/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while StarryAI scores 5/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Craiyon and StarryAI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Craiyon's free tier and StarryAI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
